# ============================================================
# .cursorrules — ООО «Умная зарядка» (tts64.ru)
# Project: Lead-generation & image website for TSS/Pandora dealer
# Architecture: Next.js 14 App Router + PostgreSQL + Prisma
# Last updated: 2025-03-21
# ============================================================
#
# Canonical copy: keep this file only at the app root (smart-charging/.cursorrules).
# Do not duplicate under a parent folder — Cursor loads rules from the workspace root;
# open the smart-charging/ folder as the workspace to apply these rules.
#
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PROJECT CONTEXT
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# This project is a B2B/B2C website for "Умная зарядка" LLC — an official 
# dealer of TSS (power generators) and Pandora (EV charging stations) 
# based in Saratov, Russia.
#
# Primary goal: generate 10+ leads/month via organic search traffic.
# Secondary goal: establish brand credibility and expertise.
#
# The site has NO e-commerce checkout flow. It is a catalog + lead forms site.
# There is NO CRM. All leads go to a Telegram bot + manager email.
#
# Target domain: tts64.ru
# Hosting: Beget VPS (Docker deployment)
# Language of UI: Russian (ru-RU)
# Language of code: English (variables, functions, comments)

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TECH STACK (strict — do NOT substitute)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Framework:        Next.js 14.x (App Router ONLY — no Pages Router)
# Language:         TypeScript 5.x (strict mode enabled)
# Runtime:          Node.js 20 LTS
# Database:         PostgreSQL 16
# ORM:              Prisma 5.x
# Styling:          Tailwind CSS 3.4 (NO CSS Modules, NO styled-components)
# UI primitives:    Headless UI + custom components (NO Material UI, NO Ant Design, NO Chakra)
# Forms:            React Hook Form + Zod (shared schemas for client + server)
# Auth:             NextAuth.js v5 (Auth.js) — credentials provider ONLY
# Rich text editor: TipTap (admin panel content editing)
# Email:            Nodemailer (Beget SMTP)
# Telegram:         grammy library
# Images:           next/image with Sharp (auto WebP)
# Icons:            lucide-react
# Analytics:        @next/third-parties for Yandex.Metrika + GA4 (loaded via Script)
# Animations:       Framer Motion (sparingly — performance first)
# Package manager:  pnpm (NOT npm, NOT yarn)
# Linting:          ESLint (next/core-web-vitals + typescript rules)
# Formatting:       Prettier (with tailwind plugin)
# Containerization: Docker + docker-compose (PostgreSQL + Next.js app)

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# FILE STRUCTURE (enforce strictly)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

